1.
a. create bond
b. add vni
c. add member link to bond.
d. Check mac learning it should be flow based.


2.
a. Create bond
b. add vni
c. add member link to bond
d. check mac learning it should be flow based.
e. remove member link from bond.
f. configure vlan trunk/access.
g. check mac learning it should be for physical port.
h. renove vlan trunk/access.
i. add member link to bond
j. check mac learning it should be flow based.


3.
a. Create bond
b. add vni
c. add member link to bond
d. check mac learning it should be flow based.
e. Add another member link to bond.
f. Check mac learning on new member link should be flow based.
